# Assignment 2

## Block Port 80 and 443

### Aim

To block HTTP and HTTPS ports and observe browser behavior.

### Ports Blocked

| Port | Service |
| ---- | ------- |
| 80   | HTTP    |
| 443  | HTTPS   |

### Procedure

1. Open Windows Firewall.
2. Create outbound rule.
3. Block Port 80.
4. Block Port 443.
5. Open browser.
6. Attempt to access websites.

### Observation

Websites failed to load due to blocked web traffic ports.

### Result

Successfully blocked HTTP and HTTPS traffic.

